{"tid":58843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆墨玉發生恐襲　2死3傷主要是幹部","createTime":"2016-12-29T07:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T10:59:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abc0d28f07027419e837c4657890b521b297e018","tid":58843,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-29-2016/34892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-29-2016%2F34892&d=wIsT1otLT%2FLa6DRoCHtl%2F2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=7350bbf6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-29-2016/34892</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據《新華社》今日（12月29)報道，指新疆墨玉縣發生一宗恐怖襲擊，造成2人死亡，3人受傷，主要是幹部官員。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》指，從公安部取得消息，指昨日下午約4時50分，有3名暴徒駕車衝入新疆維吾爾自治區墨玉縣縣委大院，並持刀襲擊工作人員，以及引爆爆炸裝置。當場造成1名幹部和1名保安員死亡，3名幹部受輕傷。<br />\n<br />\n而3名暴徒當場被擊斃，當局正在進一步調查事件。"},{"pid":"79792fa7de7bd5d318557e4afc457f74b90a7b1b","tid":58843,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7bb429ba04d4a89a07055b2ba6c0ab09e12524","tid":58843,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"其實乜撚嘢叫幹部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屬於咩機關又唁講"},{"pid":"c904ff127e32799c877051a759134f3281f85fde","tid":58843,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f945d82e7b4f743c5fb3a09d64b7fb6b905138","tid":58843,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"香港市民齊發賀電熱烈鼓掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk